test_even_range:
assert [64] == [130, 132, 134]
  At index 0 diff: 64 != 130
  Right contains 2 more items, first extra item: 132
  Full diff:
  - [130, 132, 134]
  + [64]
test_large_range:
assert [64, 65] == [65, 66, 67]
  At index 0 diff: 64 != 65
  Right contains one more item: 67
  Full diff:
  - [65, 66, 67]
  + [64, 65]
